Planmed Logo Planmed Oy, established in 1989, is a Finnish company that designs and manufactures imaging systems and accessories for mammography as well as for orthopedic imaging. The company is headquartered in Helsinki, Finland, and exports over 98% of its production to approximately 70 countries worldwide. Planmed’s products are sold through a network of dealers. Planmed has a subsidiary in the United States and a sales office in the Netherlands. Source
